name: Work From Home Jumpsuit
description:
Sylvia was a designer, specializing in branding. She was highly regarded by her colleagues at the design firm YH Associates, where she spent a large part of her career.It was here that she learned her passion for mentorship and guiding people through their personal and professional growth. She worked her way up to a senior-- creative director role 
and won several awards for her designs. This jumpsuit was a custom design.
